column5: LOL how is he going to get it home tow truck perhaps!
Not really sure about the legality of beaching that GG... but that is a good pic.
That's one heck of a Jewfish!
They are now called Goliath Groupers bassman... somebody got their noses bent out of shape about the other name and they changed it.
The is one BIIIIIG Fish!!! That mouth is big enough for me, a recliner and a projection TV to fit in....WOW!
WOW....I HEARD THOSE GROUPERS ARE YUMMY.....MMMMMMMMM WITH GARLIC BUTTER & SPICES......cheers
There are some sources that claim that is the fish that swallowed Jonah of Biblical times.
I knew somebody would try and photoshop my picture.....
man i thought that was fake!
Goliath Groupers are a highly protected species nowadays... they've been overfished to near extinction, but are making a nice comeback since sanctions have been imposed.
big time... they are on alot of the reefs and eating alot
